00:06:18.053 --> 00:06:25.193
Bernie Ecclestone’s genius was to convince all of the teams in Formula One to sign an agreement,

00:06:25.433 --> 00:06:31.933
called The Concorde Agreement, that required them to take part in the race for the upcoming season.

00:06:32.973 --> 00:06:39.033
He could then go to TV networks all over the world and say “look, we know

00:06:39.083 --> 00:06:43.583
