00:07:23.103 --> 00:07:28.353
rest was distributed to the teams and an organisation called the Fédération

00:07:28.353 --> 00:07:34.403
Internationale de l’Automobile, the FIA, which was the governing body of the sport.

00:07:35.893 --> 00:07:43.393
