00:08:10.923 --> 00:08:15.873
received complete control of all of the commercial rights of Formula One.

00:08:16.913 --> 00:08:19.723
It was the best deal of his life.

00:08:20.543 --> 00:08:27.503
He negotiated agreements with TV companies all over the world, taking Formula One away from its

00:08:27.803 --> 00:08:34.523
historical base in Western Europe and opening it up in new markets in China and the Middle East.

00:08:35.653 --> 00:08:41.083
It grew and grew, and with it grew Mr Ecclestone’s bank balance.

00:08:41.953 --> 00:08:46.933
